# Pixel Art: FreelanceFlow Logo

**File:** `freelanceflow-logo.png`
**Dimensions:** 64x64 pixels
**Format:** PNG

## Description

A pixel art representation of the FreelanceFlow platform — a stylized briefcase with a flowing checkmark, symbolizing completed freelance jobs. Uses a vibrant purple (#8B5CF6) and teal (#14B8A6) palette on a dark background to match the app's modern branding.

## Why

This logo captures the core identity of FreelanceFlow: empowering freelancers to find work and clients to hire talent efficiently. The briefcase represents work/projects, while the flowing checkmark signifies successful task completion — the "flow" in FreelanceFlow.